#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:248 index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "The note length"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"and click on a note line. If you click near an existing note a chord is "
"created. If you click on an existing note the note is removed. To delete a "
"note you can also use the backspace key. To delete a single note from chord "
"use the <userinput>DEL</userinput> key."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to insert a note with an accidental choose an accidental on 2nd "
