#: index.docbook:682 index.docbook:1750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The difference is the MIDI mapping. The first form - signed with \"1\" - "
"maps the note lines to pitches like the treble clef would map. The 2nd form "
"- signed with \"2\" - maps note lines to pitches like the bass clef would "
"map. The difference is not visible."
