"the different voices by selecting one of the radio buttons <userinput>1</"
"userinput>, <userinput>2</userinput>, <userinput>3</userinput>, or "
"<userinput>4</userinput>. Choose a sound, a volume, and a stereo position "
"(pan) of each voice."
