"inlinemediaobject>). If you now place the mouse at a certain position on a "
"staff the notes you play on midikeyboard are inserted. <emphasis>Note!</"
"emphasis> The keys determine the pitch not the length! The length of the "
"notes are set like described in <link linkend=\"insert_notes\">Inserting/"
"Deleting notes</link>."
